&lt;p&gt;In addition to our innovative technology and solutions, our people are vital to our success. Our team has the ambition to help internationally trading companies regain control of their payments by making the market open and transparent. By responding to the wishes and needs of the customer, you know how to translate our products into the best possible solution and use. By providing the customer with insight into exchange rates, various currencies and the simplicity of multi-currency payments, you give them the confidence to further strengthen and expand their international presence. You act as a sparring partner and can switch quickly between various tasks and responsibilities. You are the point of contact for the customer.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You are responsible for the entire sales cycle; from lead generation and prospecting to closing the deal and onboarding. By building a strong network and extensive knowledge of the FX market, you help clients achieve strategic objectives.&lt;/p&gt;
